SEARCH
Package workers

Class Record

java.lang.Object
workers.Record
public class Record extends Object
Represents a musical record to be indexed. Fields are automatically mapped and flattened for Elasticsearch. Includes both textual and array representations of interval and measure mappings.

The names of these fields correspond DIRECTLY to method processes of ElasticProcessor.

  • Field Details

    • name

      private String name

    • intervals_text

      private String intervals_text
      Contains one less than the number of notes, as this is the half-step distance between notes e.g. if the first four notes are C, C, D, C#, this string starts with the three intervals "0 2 -1 ..."

    • measure_map

      private String measure_map
      It is a one-to-one mapping of note number -> measure number it belongs to e.g. if there are exactly four notes in the first measure, this string begins with "0 0 0 0 1 ..."

    • intervals_as_array

      private int[] intervals_as_array
      Contains one less than the number of notes, as this is the half-step distance between notes e.g. if the first four notes are C, C, D, C#, this array starts with the three intervals [0, 2, -1, ...]

    • measure_map_as_array

      private int[] measure_map_as_array
      It is a one-to-one mapping of note number -> measure number it belongs to e.g. if there are exactly four notes in the first measure, this array begins with [0, 0, 0, 0, 1, ...]
